{"tid":763783,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"點睇每次同女友嘈交佢都同個狗公數你","createTime":"2018-08-01T11:44:26.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-01T13:11:10.000Z","uid":39233,"like":19,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"06961e2d304364b49c96c2c6495857074e4256ac","tid":763783,"uid":39233,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-01T11:44:26.000Z","msg":"每次嘈交同唔滿意，佢都會係我面前攞部手機出黎搵個狗公唱衰我數臭我<br />\n有咩都係我地既事，點解要四圍唱呢？<br />\n平時出街機不離手我都算，係咪需要係我面前同第二個男人抹黑我先？同佢平心靜氣講我唔中意，佢就屈我我都搵女唱佢然後刪紀錄，係咪咁樣會令自己好過啲<br />\n我自己根本冇朋友，想搵個人傾下心事都冇，何況女？"},{"pid":"3a17b927cfe9b819e704134c3805320d70ba1eca","tid":763783,"uid":11462,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-01T11:45:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/green_cap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0567b288fb36e25b00dec1e92feed20e6e9f6e56","tid":763783,"uid":103212,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-01T11:46:00.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"073f019f975e1115374f14472d024fabda294654","tid":763783,"uid":30098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-01T11:46:47.000Z","msg":"臭雞黎"},{"pid":"da365b41996d8a0813a0500181ccd6ce6ae4bd99","tid":763783,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-01T11:47:14.000Z","msg":"g lor"},{"pid":"cb78c5f983a3243bb220daa74e5c4f1f9fb8d441","tid":763783,"uid":140798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-01T11:47:28.000Z","msg":"佢地有路"},{"pid":"aa3a7091851fc1189d695d19b27c174aed0b9c72","tid":763783,"uid":179679,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-01T11:49:15.000Z","msg":"咁樣通常已經扑左十幾鑊"},{"pid":"c165ffdf3fa77918c7641271a6999226aa104a83","tid":763783,"uid":39233,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"quote":{"pid":"0567b288fb36e25b00dec1e92feed20e6e9f6e56","tid":763783,"uid":103212,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-01T11:46:00.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-01T11:49:19.000Z","msg":"的確，但如果係唔分開